Class HtmlPages

java.lang.Object
no.hiof.webframework.application.frontend.HtmlPages
All Implemented Interfaces:
IHtmlPage
public class HtmlPages extends Object implements IHtmlPage
This class contains pre-built HTML pages for a web application. It implements the IHtmlPage interface.
